The ultimate dream would be to see Aahad Nayani sir vs Darshan Doshi sir.
Well..Not exactly versus, but both doing a jam! :)

Nevertheless, an amazing track of Allah Hoo...one of the best versions ever heard. I'd have to agree, rock is at its best when a sufi is converted.
Note: Watch 'Akheeyan Udeek diyan' at Nescafe Basement, yet another exemplary display of Sufi Rock.
